-- Inserting Kiddie Meals
('Kiddie Spaghetti Bolognese + Lemonade', 'Imagine a heaping plate of golden, crispy French fries, perfectly seasoned and cooked to a delightful crunch. Topped generously with a rich and savory chicken Bolognese sauce, the sauce is a hearty blend of tender ground chicken, aromatic herbs, and a velvety tomato base, simmered to perfection. Melted mozzarella cheese cascades over the top, creating a creamy, gooey layer that adds a deliciously indulgent touch. As you dig in, each bite offers a satisfying contrast of textures—crispy fries, savory sauce, and gooey cheese—all melding together for a comfort food experience that’s both familiar and exciting.', 10.99, 'Kiddie Meals', 'Images/Kiddie/KidBologneseLemonade.png'),
('Kiddie Mac & Cheese + Lemonade', 'Kids love our Mac and Cheese! Treat yours with a perfectly portioned Kids'' Mac and Cheese and a fresh and tasty Lemonade.', 10.99, 'Kiddie Meals', 'Images/Kiddie/KidMacLemonade.png'),
